"{\"uid\": \"myrepublica.nagariknetwork.com-news-bolt-shines-bright-wins-another-gold-in-olympic-100\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Subscribe Now RIO DE JANEIRO, Aug 15: Usain Bolt sauntered onto the track, stretched out his arms and waved his hands, signaling for more applause.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 148, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"RIO DE JANEIRO\", \"from\": 14, \"to\": 28}, {\"ngram\": \"Aug\", \"from\": 30, \"to\": 33}, {\"ngram\": \"Usain Bolt\", \"from\": 38, \"to\": 48}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 64, \"to\": 73}, {\"ngram\": \"his arms\", \"from\": 89, \"to\": 97}, {\"ngram\": \"his hands\", \"from\": 108, \"to\": 117}, {\"ngram\": \"more applause\", \"from\": 133, \"to\": 146}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He knew exactly how this night was going to go.\", \"from\": 150, \"to\": 197, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this night\", \"from\": 170, \"to\": 180}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The sprinter-turned-showman's swan song in the Olympic 100 meters Sunday night was a no-doubter - a pedestrian-by-his-standards 9.81-second sprint down the straightaway, but not so slow that he could not take time to point at his own chest with his thumb a step before he crossed the finish line.\", \"from\": 199, \"to\": 495, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The sprinter-turned-showman's swan song\", \"from\": 199, \"to\": 238}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic 100 meters\", \"from\": 242, \"to\": 264}, {\"ngram\": \"-standards\", \"from\": 316, \"to\": 326}, {\"ngram\": \"the straightaway\", \"from\": 351, \"to\": 367}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 408, \"to\": 412}, {\"ngram\": \"his own chest\", \"from\": 425, \"to\": 438}, {\"ngram\": \"his thumb\", \"from\": 444, \"to\": 453}, {\"ngram\": \"the finish line\", \"from\": 479, \"to\": 494}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was brilliant,\\\" Bolt said.\", \"from\": 497, \"to\": 527, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Bolt\", \"from\": 517, \"to\": 521}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I did not go so fast but I am so happy I won.\", \"from\": 528, \"to\": 574, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I told you guys I was going to do it.\\\"\", \"from\": 575, \"to\": 613, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"guys\", \"from\": 586, \"to\": 590}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He won his record-setting third straight title in track's featured event and his seventh Olympic gold.\", \"from\": 615, \"to\": 717, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his record-setting third straight title\", \"from\": 622, \"to\": 661}, {\"ngram\": \"track's featured event\", \"from\": 665, \"to\": 687}, {\"ngram\": \"his seventh Olympic gold\", \"from\": 692, \"to\": 716}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He has already swept aside pretty much every sprinter who had any claim on being the greatest.\", \"from\": 719, \"to\": 813, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"every sprinter\", \"from\": 758, \"to\": 772}, {\"ngram\": \"any claim\", \"from\": 781, \"to\": 790}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, on a muggy night in Rio, Bolt took aim at Michael Phelps and the Olympics themselves, shoving the swimmer and all his 23 medals to the background and making this official: The Bolt Games have begun.\", \"from\": 815, \"to\": 1017, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 839, \"end\": 842, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7864103586415546e-20, \"text\": \"Rio\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2016_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 861, \"end\": 875, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.126595184033404e-59, \"text\": \"Michael Phelps\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Phelps\"}], \"noun_phrases\"